HEADWORD: Passionless
<hw>Pas"sion*less</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Void of passion;
without anger or emotion; not easily excited; calm.</def>
⟦ldquo⟧Self-contained and <xex>passionless</xex>.⟦rdquo⟧
<rj><au>Tennyson.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

